      "lesson title": "Using AI in Client Reports Safely",
      "order": 1,
      "Description": "This lesson introduces practical guidance for using AI tools responsibly when preparing client reports and other professional deliverables. You will learn how to identify the risks of sharing sensitive client information with AI tools, and how to put simple safeguards in place to prevent data leakage. The lesson also covers how to spot and correct inaccuracies that AI tools can introduce, so that your final reports remain accurate and trustworthy. By the end, you will have a clear, beginner-friendly framework for integrating AI into your workflow without compromising client confidentiality or the quality of your work.",
